{"tid":1190162,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"十年：浮瓜","createTime":"2019-06-07T07:27:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T07:54:19.000Z","uid":8478,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"eba26d04a71cd88733206a5f66bcbacff2243531","tid":1190162,"uid":8478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T07:27:30.000Z","msg":"影片以黑白畫面與黑色幽默，講述當權者為了在香港推行國家安全法，自導自演了一場行刺政治人物的「恐怖襲擊」。雖然把故事設定於五年後（即2020年）的勞動節，有點不貼題，不過五年後尚猶如此，十年後可想而知。影片對「親建制」人物的影射呼之欲出，而建制政黨「真愛聯」英文簡稱「TMD」亦極盡嘲諷。導演在有限資源下，選擇簡單場景（一所學校），一開局已利落交代了三組人物（執行指令的幫會嘍囉、操控大局的政圈高層、等待被行刺的政治人物）的來龍去脈。幫會嘍囉的對話，透露了社會低下層的生活困境，終於被利誘助紂為虐。擲毫一場非常絕妙，巴哈的大提琴樂曲下，嘍囉拋出一個1997年鑄造的硬幣，決定由誰開槍，然後接上學校禮堂攤位遊戲的畫面，玩具硬幣落下，以為仍有選擇餘地可以從中圖利的嘍囉，不知道自己早已淪為棋子，選擇了出賣自己（和香港）就再無翻身的可能。<br />\n<br />\n原文：《《十年》：想像香港崩壞時》 <a href=\"https://theinitium.com/article/20151219-culture-column-chanchiwa/?utm_medium=copy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheinitium.com%2Farticle%2F20151219-culture-column-chanchiwa%2F%3Futm_medium%3Dcopy&d=SmQqe2lJFulj5u2s5Cv8uhR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=7a9025e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://theinitium.com/article/20151219-culture-column-chanchiwa/?utm_medium=copy</a> <br />\n&copy; 端傳媒 Initium Media"},{"pid":"ca1a16e591712f70b91b62995245995931d53e12","tid":1190162,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T07:28:48.000Z","msg":"成件事自編自導<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e5f287692c4b77a92f6d194b8d696028e6e8226","tid":1190162,"uid":8478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T07:37:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bcf557bf1f94840288e6900b04c82b78cf5ccbd","tid":1190162,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T07:40:56.000Z","msg":"其實係預言劇嚟"},{"pid":"0cc9b5855b645c0b83a584d694427d90186b67ef","tid":1190162,"uid":8478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T07:54:19.000Z","msg":"如果香港人少少事都縮 遲早講廣東話同賣蛋都犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}